definitions.definition: a line (of seaweed or differently coloured sand etc) on the shore showing the level of high or low tide
any mark showing the limit of some past activity
a line of scum left on a bath tub when the water is drained away

main_definition: a line (of seaweed or differently coloured sand etc) on the shore showing the level of high or low tide
secondary_definitions: ( by extension ) any mark showing the limit of some past activity
( humorous ) a line of scum left on a bath tub when the water is drained away
